<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #10B981; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .details { background-color: #F3F4F6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Donation Received!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for your generous donation. Your contribution helps us make a real difference.</p>
      
      <div class="details">
        <p><strong>Donation ID:</strong> {{donationId}}</p>
        <p><strong>Item Category:</strong> {{category}}</p>
        <p><strong>Quantity:</strong> {{quantity}} {{unit}}</p>
        <p><strong>NGO:</strong> {{ngoName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>You have earned <strong>{{points}} points</strong> for this donation!</p>
      <p>We will notify you when the NGO processes your donation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} SevaSetu. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
